algun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC911;&#xC5D0;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBB38;&#xC81C;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBC1C;&#xC0DD;&#xC744;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC10;&#xC9C0;&#xD558;&#xBA74;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB2E4;&#xC2DC;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> ver1</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB85C;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB864;&#xBC31;&#xC2DC;&#xD0A4;&#xB294;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC83;&#xC774;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC00;&#xB2A5;&#xD558;&#xB2E4;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">.</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">Canary/Linear <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBC30;&#xD3EC;</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;color:#0432ff;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;text-decoration:underline\">Canary/Linear </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;color:#0432ff;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;text-decoration:underline\">&#xBC30;&#xD3EC;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;color:#0432ff;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;text-decoration:underline\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;color:#0432ff;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic;text-decoration:underline\">&#xCC38;&#xACE0;&#xC0AC;&#xC774;&#xD2B8;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;color:#0432ff;font-weight:bold\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;color:#70ad47;font-weight:bold\"> </span><a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/lambda/latest/dg/automating-updates-to-serverless-apps.html\" lang=\"ko-KR\">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/lambda/latest/dg/automating-updates-to-serverless-apps.html</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"e Deployments Deployment d-ZFANAY15T \nDeployment: d.ZFANAY15T \nDeployment In progress \nDeployment details \nstat us \" width=\"480\" height=\"301\" src=\"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/resources/0-3c25b56d15136b4198ba1240e58a33ee!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2018/content?publicAuth=true&amp;mimeType=image/png\" data-src-type=\"image/png\" data-fullres-src=\"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/resources/0-3c25b56d15136b4198ba1240e58a33ee!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2018/content?publicAuth=true&amp;mimeType=image/png\" data-fullres-src-type=\"image/png\">\n\t\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC544;&#xB798;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC11C;&#xBE44;&#xC2A4;&#xB97C;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD1B5;&#xD574;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC124;&#xC815;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC00;&#xB2A5;&#xD558;&#xB2E4;</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">AWS CodeDeploy</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:circle\"><span